  - [LOW] 3M Company filed a patent infringement lawsuit against Elo Touch Solutions in November 2025, alleging infringement of multiple patents related to projected capacitive touch screen and metal mesh conductor technology.
  - [INFO] Zebra Technologies announced its intent to acquire Elo Touch Solutions for $1.3 billion in cash, expanding its self-service and interactive display offerings.
